    "en": {
      "title": "Organized criminals distribute vouchers for the competition",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A senior police officer said that gift vouchers were distributed in Matugama to celebrate the birthday of an organized criminal Shan Arosh Jayasinghe alias Matugama Shan who is hiding abroad.",
        "Over 300 low-income people have been given 5000 rupees vouchers, which enable them to buy goods at a super market, at the residence of Jivan Withana Mawatha, Aluthgama Road, Matugama, by Shan Namatta's wife.",
        "It is also known that vouchers are going to be given to another hundred people soon.",
        "On the advice of Matugama Shan, the wife of Shan, who was arrested by the police for aiding and abetting the incident of shooting and killing a woman on Matugama Balika Road, was remanded and released on bail about 3 weeks ago. According to police sources, Imahat Harasarin was welcomed and brought home wearing necklaces."
      ],
